name.zh-Hans: 苏阳和紫山地铁线路图

desc.zh-Hans:
注：此地图仅供参考请勿商用，需要使用到我这线路图的朋友可以b站先私我再使用噢，但禁止盗图，b站名：晨鳄灰
这两城市的名字都是我虚构的，在我这里的苏阳和紫山就类似国内一些互相通地铁的城市（譬如广州-佛山，上海-苏州等等）本人做图用时长，花了点心血，如果喜欢的朋友可以下载参考或者自行修改不过得要和作者先说明，以免产生不必要的麻烦，谢谢(*^_^*)
desc.en:
Note: This map is for reference only and should not be used for commercial purposes. Friends who need to use my route map can use it privately at Bilibili first, but stealing the map is prohibited.Bilibili name: 晨鳄灰
I made up the names of these two cities. Suyang and Zishan here are similar to some cities in China that connect with each other by subway (such as Guangzhou Foshan, Shanghai Suzhou, etc.). I spent a lot of time and effort in drawing. If you like friends, you can download references or modify them yourself, but you need to explain to the author first to avoid unnecessary trouble. Thank you (* ^ _ ^ *)
